<item>
            <title>[LU-810] Fix helpers for reading flags in HSM changelog records</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-810</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since Lustre 2.0, Lustre include has macros to read flags from HSM changelog records.&lt;br/&gt;
There are buggy. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached patch fixes them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
